Retrieve all preferred activities, previously added with addPreferredActivity, that are currently registered with the system. Params: outFilters – A required list in which to place the filters of all of the preferred activities. outActivities – A required list in which to place the component names of all of the preferred activities. packageName – An optional package in which you would like to limit the list. If null, all activities will be returned; if non-null, only those activities in the given package are returned. Returns: Returns the total number of registered preferred activities (the number of distinct IntentFilter records, not the number of unique activity components) that were found.
